---
title: Nacho Style Loaded Fries and Tomato Salsa with 'Queso' Cheese Sauce and Chipotle Black Beans
description: Load up on flavour with our Nacho Style Loaded Fries and Tomato Salsa for a delicious veggie dinner. The main flavour here comes from chipotle, full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R41_W38_UK_V20152-4_Main_low_2-104209e0.jpg
